Title : Template:Esccnty
Text : [[{{{1}}} in {{#switch: {{{2|}}} 
| Junior
| JESC = the Junior Eurovision Song Contest
| Dance
| EDC = the Eurovision Dance Contest
| Musicians
| EYM = the Eurovision Young Musicians
| Dancers
| EYD = the Eurovision Young Dancers
| Choir = Eurovision Choir
| Asia = the Eurovision Asia Song Contest
| the Eurovision Song Contest}} {{{y|}}}|{{#if: {{{t|<noinclude>-</noinclude>}}}|{{{t|}}}|{{{1|}}}}}]]<noinclude>

Makes links to individual Eurovision Song Contest countries easier to type.

'''Using the template:'''<br/> 
* <nowiki>{{Esccnty|Denmark}}</nowiki> → [[Denmark in the Eurovision Song Contest|Denmark]]
* <nowiki>{{Esccnty|Denmark|y=2014}}</nowiki> → [[Denmark in the Eurovision Song Contest 2014|Denmark]]
* <nowiki>{{Esccnty|Denmark||t=Danish}}</nowiki> → [[Denmark in the Eurovision Song Contest|Danish]]
* <nowiki>{{Esccnty|Denmark|y=2014|t=Danish}}</nowiki> → [[Denmark in the Eurovision Song Contest 2014|Danish]]
* <nowiki>{{Esccnty|Denmark|Junior}}</nowiki> → [[Denmark in the Junior Eurovision Song Contest|Denmark]]
* <nowiki>{{Esccnty|Denmark|Dance}}</nowiki> → [[Denmark in the Eurovision Dance Contest|Denmark]]
* <nowiki>{{Esccnty|Denmark|Musicians}}</nowiki> → [[Denmark in the Eurovision Young Musicians|Denmark]]
* <nowiki>{{Esccnty|Denmark|Dancers}}</nowiki> → [[Denmark in the Eurovision Young Dancers|Denmark]]
* <nowiki>{{Esccnty|Denmark|Choir}}</nowiki> → [[Denmark in Eurovision Choir|Denmark]]
* <nowiki>{{Esccnty|Denmark|Asia}}</nowiki> → [[Australia in the Eurovision Asia Song Contest|Australia]]
{{pp-template}}
[[Category:Eurovision Song Contest templates|{{PAGENAME}}]]
</noinclude>
